68
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:50,020
I didn’t know princess was playing it.

69
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:55,620
Huaiji,

70
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:57,940
go tell him.

71
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:05,620
Go ahead.

72
00:05:13,100 --> 00:05:13,900
Mr. Cao,

73
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:15,700
princess said

74
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:18,380
although you two are cousins

75
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:20,420
and used to be playmates,

76
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:22,100
