77
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,540
You should keep a distance from each other.

78
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:25,660
Princess is His Majesty’s eldest daughter

79
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,020
while you’re the Empress’s nephew.

80
00:05:28,580 --> 00:05:29,580
The noble

81
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,940
