82
00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:39,300
Please behave yourself.

83
00:06:15,540 --> 00:06:16,820
Everyone is waiting for her!

84
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,580
Isn’t she sick?

85
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:23,260
Has she ever not?

86
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:49,860
She’s wearing lantern silk again.

87
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:52,180
Hasn’t His Majesty banned it?

88
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:53,740
= Wen Yanbo’s Wife =
Back then,

89
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,660
Prime Minister Wen lost his post because of it.

90
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:57,300
Could it be

91
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,700
that he’s reinstated?

92
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:01,540
Are they still on the same side?

93
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:03,740
It’s...

94
00:07:05,870 --> 00:07:07,080
Don’t know.

95
00:07:10,340 --> 00:07:12,540
Are you feeling better, Noble Consort?

96
00:07:12,890 --> 00:07:14,590
Once His Majesty sees you here

97
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:16,100
to celebrate his birthday,

98
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:18,540
he won’t need

99
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:19,770
any other presents.

100
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:24,080
Your Highness, you do have a way with words.

101
00:07:36,650 --> 00:07:37,630
His Majesty has arrived.

102
00:07:58,180 --> 00:07:59,340
Princess, you’re going to

103
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,380
play the instrument

104
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,260
at His Majesty’s birthday banquet later.

105
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:06,940
Don’t hurt your fingers.

106
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:11,020
You did that on purpose,

107
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:13,420
