112
00:08:28,780 --> 00:08:30,460
I asked you to say a few things to him,

113
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,500
but how come you forgot

114
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:34,540
the line after

115
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:36,380
“Princess is His Majesty’s eldest daughter”?

116
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:38,900
That she’s different from showgirls.

117
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:45,620
I forgot that by accident.

118
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:48,780
Please punish me.

119
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:54,380
You omitted it on purpose!

120
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:57,340
I knew it!

121
00:08:58,940 --> 00:08:59,740
You thought

122
00:08:59,740 --> 00:09:00,980
saying that to him

123
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:03,020
and hinting that Lu Yingniang

124
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:04,820
would make me look jealous.

125
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:08,060
All these years, I still couldn’t let that go.

126
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:10,700
A princess should have a big heart.

127
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:16,020
It was inappropriate to say that to him,

128
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:19,100
right?

129
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:23,250
♪ Isolated kite ♪

130
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:24,500
It was improper,

131
00:09:24,650 --> 00:09:25,850
♪ Left everything behind ♪

132
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:27,420
wasn’t it?

133
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,870
♪ Lost soul ♪

134
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,730
♪ Can’t feel cause he can’t love ♪

135
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:32,420
No.

136
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:35,380
You’re elegant and graceful, princess.

137
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:39,340
His Majesty and Her Highness

138
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:41,700
will be proud of you.

139
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:45,320
♪ And nourishes all living things ♪

140
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:52,760
♪ Those who love more are always
hurt by who love less ♪

141
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,050
♪ I don’t want to remember, but I can’t forget ♪

142
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:54,940
I’ve never

143
00:09:58,580 --> 00:10:00,060
forgotten the day

144
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:04,820
he and that string player

145
00:10:06,660 --> 00:10:07,700
were playing Serenade of Peaceful Joy together

146
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:11,540
