147
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:14,540
I am jealous.

148
00:10:15,610 --> 00:10:20,390
♪ Light it up for the people ♪

149
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:26,240
♪ Cure the heartless injury ♪

150
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:28,700
Princess.

151
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,980
Thank you, Huaiji.

152
00:10:58,180 --> 00:10:59,860
You always look out for me.

153
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:05,340
Other than you,

154
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,500
no one has seen me

155
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:11,020
