156
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:35,820
You look great today.

157
00:11:36,980 --> 00:11:38,060
Are you getting better?

158
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:41,900
The same as before.

159
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:44,540
I guess the dress I’m wearing graces me.

160
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:47,940
Is it made of the lantern silk

161
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:49,660
Yanbo’s wife gave you?

162
00:11:51,060 --> 00:11:52,020
Back then,

163
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:54,140
although Prime Minister Wen asked his wife

164
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:56,580
to give this silk to me,

165
00:11:57,740 --> 00:11:59,580
