166
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:00,460
for Your Majesty

167
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:02,900
to show his loyalty.

168
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,660
Today is Your Majesty’s birthday.

169
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,460
I spent days

170
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:09,500
looking for a birthday present for you,

171
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:10,900
but failed to find an appropriate one.

172
00:12:12,070 --> 00:12:13,340
After consideration,

173
00:12:13,980 --> 00:12:16,540
I thought everything I own came from Your Majesty.

174
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:19,170
I have nothing

175
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:20,220
to give you in return,

176
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:22,380
so I could only wear

177
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:23,460
this silk dress for you.

178
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,780
If it makes me presentable,

179
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:29,300
then my effort won’t be in vain.

180
00:12:59,940 --> 00:13:01,260
This dress is gorgeous

181
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:04,980
but the gold embroidery is extravagant.

182
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:07,340
Today is an exception,

183
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:09,580
but don’t wear it again.

184
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:14,260
Yes, Your Majesty.

185
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:18,300
I won’t

186
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:22,700
wear it ever again.

187
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:53,060
Princess Fukang presents harp music

188
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,420
to celebrate Your Majesty’s birthday.

189
00:13:57,860 --> 00:14:02,780
= Winehouse Fan =

190
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:05,540
This is the finest liquor

191
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:06,620
I made.

192
00:14:07,540 --> 00:14:09,060
The ingredients and techniques

193
00:14:09,180 --> 00:14:10,580
can’t be found elsewhere.

194
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:11,660
I assure you

195
00:14:11,780 --> 00:14:13,740
there isn’t another jar like this

196
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:14,660
in the entire city.

197
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,900
In this jar

198
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:20,100
is the 20-year-old wine from the west.

199
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:21,420
I bought it there

200
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,700
a long time ago.

201
00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:25,260
= Liang Yuansheng =
I’m serving you these today

202
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,140
to celebrate His Majesty’s birthday

203
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:30,260
and Mr. Han’s return.

204
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:34,300
I’m not transferred back.

205
00:14:34,660 --> 00:14:36,020
Thanks to His Majesty’s kindness,

206
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:38,500
I could be here to celebrate his birthday.

207
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:39,940
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =

208
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:40,900
Right after you arrived,

209
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:43,460
His Majesty summoned you alone

210
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:44,980
before the celebration.

211
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:47,980
Your transfer will soon become official.

212
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:51,180
- Is Mr. Han here? - Am I right?

213
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:55,860
General Di.

214
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:04,580
To welcome Mr. Han back,

215
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:05,780
this meal is on me.

216
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:09,380
= Di Qing, courtesy name Hanchen =
Serve more jars of the finest liquor.

217
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:12,860
= Han Qi, courtesy name Zhigui =

218
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:15,060
General Di.

219
00:15:16,780 --> 00:15:18,220
Mr. Han, here,

220
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:28,780
a toast to you.

221
00:15:37,740 --> 00:15:38,980
Chief Di, I suppose

222
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:41,740
this isn’t just to welcome me back.

223
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:43,660
I dare not drink it.

224
00:15:44,980 --> 00:15:46,460
I must say

225
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:47,500
you’re indeed sharp.

226
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:50,060
I do need a favor.

227
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:54,900
I’m all ears.

228
00:15:56,460 --> 00:15:57,540
A soldier of mine

229
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:59,340
survived the battle against Yuanhao

230
00:15:59,380 --> 00:16:00,980
when he was a teenager.

231
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:02,660
When squashing the revolt in Guangxi,

232
00:16:02,740 --> 00:16:03,860
he was exceptionally gallant.

233
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:08,020
Lately, I heard he’s imprisoned

234
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:11,340
for his offense in Dingzhou pending for sentence.

235
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:13,860
Please be lenient with him.

236
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:17,060
He’s a decorated war hero,

237
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:18,700
a rare talent.

238
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:20,700
Mr. Han,

239
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:23,260
please let him go.

240
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:32,700
Chief Di,

241
00:16:33,940 --> 00:16:35,420
I only know

242
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:38,820
those who passed the exam as top scholars

243
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:40,860
are regarded as heroes

244
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:42,780
and talents.

245
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:41,980
Princess’s beauty is growing with time.

246
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:45,100
She’s fairylike when playing the instrument.

247
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:47,500
My son Wei

248
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:49,220
is such a lucky boy.

249
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:51,340
Sadly, his father

250
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:53,500
didn’t get to see him getting married...

251
00:17:55,420 --> 00:17:57,660
They’re just meant to be.

252
00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:00,660
As fair as princess is,

253
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:03,300
= Li Wei’s Mother, Yang =
she ate a lot when she was little.

254
00:18:03,860 --> 00:18:05,420
She even sat on my son’s shoulders

255
00:18:05,900 --> 00:18:06,820
to pick up candied fruit.

256
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:10,260
Aren’t they childhood sweethearts?

257
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:13,900
Back then, she was...

258
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:19,300
I’ve been practicing for years

259
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:22,820
and finally had the courage

260
00:18:23,260 --> 00:18:24,740
to play this instrument today

261
00:18:25,660 --> 00:18:26,780
to celebrate father’s birthday.

262
00:18:27,900 --> 00:18:29,260
Forgive me if I didn’t play it well enough.

263
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:31,140
It was to show my love and respect for father.

264
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:34,380
May you live a long and healthy life.

265
00:18:35,020 --> 00:18:37,420
May the world be blessed with good weather.

266
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:41,580
I hope everyone can enjoy peace

267
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:43,500
and prosperity.

268
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:48,340
Good! Wonderful!

269
00:18:49,180 --> 00:18:50,140
Huirou has grown up

270
00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:51,540
and become more considerate.

271
00:18:52,620 --> 00:18:54,700
Come here. Sit next to me.

272
00:18:56,220 --> 00:18:57,260
Princess’s matured

273
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:58,860
and raised well.

274
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:01,340
Your Majesty, have you

275
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:03,500
decided on the date

276
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:05,380
of her wedding?

277
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:16,420
Huirou.

278
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:18,220
Sit next to me.

279
00:19:22,780 --> 00:19:25,460
Your Majesty, you have no other children.

280
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:28,860
There’s no good news in the harem, either.

281
00:19:30,100 --> 00:19:31,420
Once princess gets married,

282
00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:34,300
she and her husband can come together next year.

283
00:19:35,780 --> 00:19:36,740
Seeing such a perfect couple

284
00:19:37,380 --> 00:19:38,780
standing here together,

285
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:41,780
Your Majesty will be even happier.

286
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:49,100
Thank you, madam.

287
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:52,780
Your Majesty,

288
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:55,260
I’m looking forward

289
00:19:55,540 --> 00:19:57,180
to their wedding, too,

290
00:19:57,380 --> 00:19:58,900
so that they can have sons

291
00:19:58,900 --> 00:20:00,260
who will be your grandsons.

292
00:20:00,780 --> 00:20:01,980
Your Majesty, you don’t have a son,

293
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:03,700
and a grandson can sort of

294
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:04,980
make up for the loss.

295
00:20:15,060 --> 00:20:15,780
I...

296
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,300
Father, Your Highness,

297
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:29,180
please allow me to get changed.

298
00:20:30,420 --> 00:20:31,460
I’ll...

299
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:36,580
Your Majesty,

300
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,980
Huirou is having a cold.

301
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:42,220
Let her go back

302
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,560
and rest.

303
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,340
What are you still doing here?

304
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:40,020
You’re back, princess.

305
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:50,260
Since you left,

306
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:52,140
I’ve been picturing in my head

307
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:54,700
that you play the harp

308
00:21:56,260 --> 00:21:58,020
while I play the flute.

309
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:01,460
Music can speak

310
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:03,700
louder than words

311
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:04,660
if we listen carefully.

312
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:11,020
Step back!

313
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:14,260
Stay away from me.

314
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:16,700
We shouldn’t be too close. Behave yourself!

315
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:35,060
You’re a kind man, Yanguo.

316
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:37,020
Do you think I was too mean just now?

317
00:22:41,020 --> 00:22:42,140
If his request

318
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:43,180
was against the law,

319
00:22:43,180 --> 00:22:44,020
you could’ve simply turned it down.

320
00:22:44,020 --> 00:22:45,020
Why did you insult him in public

321
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:46,500
and disdain him for lacking scholarly honor?

322
00:22:47,980 --> 00:22:48,660
Are you also

323
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:49,700
one of those

324
00:22:49,780 --> 00:22:50,860
biased scholars

325
00:22:51,060 --> 00:22:51,580
who can’t stand

326
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:52,620
military officers without scholarly honor

327
00:22:52,620 --> 00:22:53,380
holding key positions

328
00:22:53,780 --> 00:22:54,980
despite the fact that they’re righteous

329
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:56,340
and decorated war heroes?

330
00:22:58,220 --> 00:22:59,460
Key posts in the Cabinet and Privy Council

331
00:23:00,060 --> 00:23:01,300
are always taken by scholars.

332
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:04,380
Generals have no right to deploy troops

333
00:23:04,700 --> 00:23:05,860
because we learned from

334
00:23:05,860 --> 00:23:06,820
the previous dynasty

335
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:08,820
and made that rule to limit generals’ power

336
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:11,220
in case they stage a coup.

337
00:23:11,220 --> 00:23:12,060
It’s a tradition.

338
00:23:13,700 --> 00:23:15,420
Officials were already shocked

339
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,620
when Di Qing became Deputy Chief of Privy Council.

340
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:18,980
Now, he’s become Chief Executive.

341
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:20,860
Di Qing was stationed at the west border for years

342
00:23:21,020 --> 00:23:22,820
and he’s with the most wins against Xixia.

343
00:23:23,820 --> 00:23:24,940
That’s why His Majesty made an exception

344
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:26,140
by promoting him to Deputy Chief.

345
00:23:26,660 --> 00:23:28,020
Besides, he crushed the revolt in Guangxi

346
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:29,620
when he was entrusted with the mission

347
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:31,660
at the time when others at the frontier

348
00:23:31,660 --> 00:23:32,620
either lost or escaped.

349
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:34,140
His victory reestablished our power.

350
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:35,100
Promoting him to Chief Executive

351
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:36,060
is fair and just.

352
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:37,980
Back then,

353
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:40,220
Di Qing stood out from the crowd

354
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,700
because of your appreciation

355
00:23:41,980 --> 00:23:43,180
and Mr. Fan’s teaching and recommendation.

356
00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:45,940
You know him well.

357
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:49,500
You think his promotion is fair and just

358
00:23:50,020 --> 00:23:51,260
but most scholars disagree

359
00:23:51,330 --> 00:23:52,540
and believe it’s too much.

360
00:23:53,220 --> 00:23:54,260
What do you think?

361
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:57,980
Di Qing’s rank alone

362
00:23:58,300 --> 00:23:59,260
doesn’t matter

363
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:00,980
but His Majesty

364
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:02,620
disregarded

365
00:24:02,620 --> 00:24:04,100
officials’ dissuasion,

366
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,020
ignored censors’ disagreements

367
00:24:07,020 --> 00:24:08,260
and insisted on changing the tradition.

368
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:14,620
So

369
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:17,980
by targeting at Di Qing,

370
00:24:18,980 --> 00:24:20,380
you and other scholars

371
00:24:20,980 --> 00:24:22,300
are actually acting against His Majesty.

372
00:24:30,420 --> 00:24:31,940
No matter His Majesty’s decision

373
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:32,780
is right or wrong,

374
00:24:33,620 --> 00:24:35,740
whether he promoted Zhang Yaozuo
because of Noble Consort

375
00:24:35,980 --> 00:24:37,340
or rewarded Di Qing

376
00:24:37,340 --> 00:24:38,580
for safeguarding the nation...

377
00:24:38,580 --> 00:24:39,740
Disregarding officials’ opinions

378
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:41,340
is wrong.

379
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:43,500
You don’t care about right or wrong.

380
00:24:44,380 --> 00:24:45,380
You simply made your own choice.

381
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:47,620
You chose to side with the majority.

382
00:24:50,020 --> 00:24:51,780
There’s no perfect policy.

383
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,140
Only if it’s accepted by most of the people

384
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:55,300
can it be pursued.

385
00:24:56,820 --> 00:24:57,540
Yanguo,

386
00:24:58,420 --> 00:25:00,100
that’s what I learnt from implementing the reform

387
00:25:00,460 --> 00:25:01,580
in the past.

388
00:25:31,100 --> 00:25:32,860
Thank you for escorting me back in the rain.

389
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:47,100
Guests and relatives are in the hall

390
00:25:48,460 --> 00:25:49,980
for father’s birthday banquet.

391
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:52,420
You aren’t a boy anymore

392
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:54,020
and shouldn’t have

393
00:25:54,020 --> 00:25:55,500
followed your parents to the inner courtyard.

394
00:25:57,140 --> 00:25:57,900
When you arrived,

395
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:00,860
rather than waiting outside

396
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:01,820
to be summoned by Her Highness,

397
00:26:02,980 --> 00:26:04,260
you wandered around in the palace.

398
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:09,900
What if others speak ill of you?

399
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:15,860
I have a question.

400
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:21,940
I won’t leave

401
00:26:23,140 --> 00:26:24,460
until it’s answered.

402
00:26:26,580 --> 00:26:28,420
I’d rather be punished

403
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,580
by His Majesty and Madam Miao

404
00:26:31,300 --> 00:26:32,260
when they come back and see me here

405
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:34,940
than be tortured every day

406
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:36,940
by not knowing the truth.

407
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:43,460
Why have you been avoiding me

408
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,620
since the Double Ninth banquet

409
00:26:45,700 --> 00:26:47,300
a few years back?

410
00:26:50,980 --> 00:26:51,820
Back then,

411
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:53,220
we were so close.

412
00:26:56,900 --> 00:26:58,380
How come we became estranged all of a sudden?

413
00:27:06,860 --> 00:27:07,660
When we were little,

414
00:27:08,500 --> 00:27:09,740
Her Highness was also my parent,

415
00:27:10,220 --> 00:27:11,580
so that made you my cousin.

416
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:14,460
Of course we could play together.

417
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:16,380
Now, we’ve grown up.

418
00:27:17,100 --> 00:27:18,500
You aren’t my brother,

419
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:20,300
so we shouldn’t be too close.

420
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:27,580
Huirou,

421
00:27:31,220 --> 00:27:33,420
His Majesty betrothed you to that rotten wood.

422
00:27:35,900 --> 00:27:37,380
But are you willing

423
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,020
to see your heart

424
00:27:41,020 --> 00:27:42,460
rot in it?

425
00:27:48,580 --> 00:27:49,420
How dare you!

426
00:28:14,130 --> 00:28:14,940
Your Majesty.

427
00:28:31,140 --> 00:28:32,260
It’s raining outside.

428
00:28:33,620 --> 00:28:34,820
Have them prepare a carriage.

429
00:28:48,980 --> 00:28:49,900
Thank you, Your Majesty.

430
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:52,140
I’ll...

431
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:55,220
go to your chamber later.

432
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:07,690
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

433
00:29:08,480 --> 00:29:15,210
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

434
00:29:15,930 --> 00:29:22,810
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

435
00:29:22,810 --> 00:29:29,720
♪ Without considering the result ♪

436
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:38,180
Am I really going to chain myself

437
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:42,380
to that rotten wood for the rest of my life?

438
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:54,060
Princess.

439
00:31:02,380 --> 00:31:03,420
Huaiji said

440
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:07,140
they’re father’s closest family.

441
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:10,980
If I’m married into that family,

442
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:14,420
they’ll treat me

443
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:16,100
as their own daughter.

444
00:31:24,100 --> 00:31:25,220
But, oh, heaven,

445
00:31:26,220 --> 00:31:27,340
you saw

446
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:30,180
my future mother-in-law.

447
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:32,260
The way she spoke

448
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:33,500
and behaved

449
00:31:35,420 --> 00:31:36,620
was utterly embarrassing.

450
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:41,820
She did shock me.

451
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:43,420
I’ve never seen anyone like her

452
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,940
in the palace.

453
00:31:46,620 --> 00:31:47,820
She did remind me

454
00:31:49,020 --> 00:31:51,300
of those women

455
00:31:51,580 --> 00:31:53,200
bargaining with shop owners

456
00:31:53,540 --> 00:31:54,130
that we saw

457
00:31:54,150 --> 00:31:56,460
outside the palace.

458
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:02,540
Princess.

459
00:32:11,580 --> 00:32:12,420
Princess.

460
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:15,220
Mr. Cao is still there.

461
00:32:17,980 --> 00:32:19,580
He’s playing the flute well.

462
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:24,060
Why don’t you join him

463
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:26,180
and play your instrument?

464
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:33,580
He and that string player

465
00:32:33,820 --> 00:32:34,940
played well together.

466
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:39,100
Why should I copy her?

467
00:32:53,300 --> 00:32:56,700
Bring him an umbrella.

468
00:33:16,580 --> 00:33:17,620
Princess asks you to leave.

469
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,220
Thank you, princess, for the umbrella.

470
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:35,580
Thank you, miss, for bringing it to me.

471
00:33:41,860 --> 00:33:42,660
Mr. Cao,

472
00:33:43,620 --> 00:33:44,780
stop playing the flute.

473
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:48,860
The more you play,

474
00:33:49,060 --> 00:33:50,340
the more princess thinks of that...

475
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:51,540
What?

476
00:33:56,900 --> 00:33:58,140
Fine, I’ll tell you.

477
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:05,820
♪ Climb the stairs barefoot
Carry shoes with gold strings ♪

478
00:34:08,240 --> 00:34:09,080
Stop.

479
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:11,680
I’m getting off.

480
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:25,800
Madam! Madam! Madam!

481
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,720
Leave me alone!

482
00:34:26,860 --> 00:34:27,660
Madam!

483
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:15,440
Your Majesty!

484
00:35:23,210 --> 00:35:23,970
Your Majesty,

485
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:26,310
am I as pretty as before?

486
00:35:27,870 --> 00:35:29,220
You’re prettier.

487
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:36,700
Madam!

488
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,490
How do you feel, madam?

489
00:35:39,490 --> 00:35:40,820
Your health is more important.

490
00:35:41,970 --> 00:35:42,570
Madam!

491
00:35:42,570 --> 00:35:44,210
Please take care of yourself, madam!

492
00:35:44,210 --> 00:35:44,830
Don’t sit on the ground.

493
00:35:44,830 --> 00:35:45,980
Please get up, madam!

494
00:35:50,740 --> 00:35:53,860
= Noble Consort Zhang died in 1054 A.D.
at the age of 31. =

495
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:55,860
= Be wailing that the past couldn’t be relived, =

496
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:57,860
= the Emperor discontinued the court
for seven days out of grief. =

497
00:35:57,860 --> 00:35:59,860
= She was buried as an empress. =

498
00:36:07,380 --> 00:36:09,500
Musician Zhang took the day off
for family business,

499
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:11,420
so I covered for her

500
00:36:11,420 --> 00:36:12,780
to play the instrument with you, princess.

501
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:28,780
Play Serenade of Peaceful Joy

502
00:36:28,780 --> 00:36:29,740
for me first.

503
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:31,260
They say

504
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:33,100
that’s what you play the best.

505
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:34,700
I want to learn from you.

506
00:36:35,740 --> 00:36:37,420
= Lu Yingniang =
I’m not as good as you say, princess.

507
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:39,020
You wowed the guests

508
00:36:39,220 --> 00:36:41,580
with that piece at His Majesty’s banquet.

509
00:36:41,980 --> 00:36:43,540
If I play it again

510
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:45,020
in front of you,

511
00:36:45,220 --> 00:36:46,220
won’t I only invite humiliation?

512
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:48,060
Don’t be so humble.

513
00:36:48,500 --> 00:36:50,860
A few years ago, after the Double Ninth banquet,

514
00:36:51,260 --> 00:36:53,180
I heard

515
00:36:53,340 --> 00:36:54,780
you and Mr. Cao

516
00:36:54,780 --> 00:36:55,700
playing this piece together in the bamboo forest.

517
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:57,780
Your coordination was so well.

518
00:36:57,900 --> 00:36:58,940
The tune was touching

519
00:36:59,380 --> 00:37:00,860
and enchanting.

520
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:04,500
I was embarrassing myself

521
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:06,700
by playing it again.

522
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:11,700
Please don’t say that.

523
00:37:11,940 --> 00:37:12,900
I don’t deserve your compliment.

524
00:37:13,660 --> 00:37:15,580
On that Double Ninth Day,

525
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:18,540
Mr. Cao looked sad

526
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:19,740
and left alone.

527
00:37:20,420 --> 00:37:21,620
I was worried

528
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,220
so I followed him out.

529
00:37:24,180 --> 00:37:24,800
Later,

530
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:27,100
he started to play the flute alone.

531
00:37:27,620 --> 00:37:28,620
Hearing that he was sorrowful,

532
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:29,780
I...

533
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:31,700
I couldn’t help comforting him,

534
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:33,500
so I asked him

535
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:35,020
to help me understand the music better

536
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:36,620
and we played it together.

537
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,900
So you followed him.

538
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:42,340
He didn’t go there to meet you.

539
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:43,620
Mr...

540
00:37:44,340 --> 00:37:45,780
Mr. Cao is beyond my reach.

541
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:48,210
Why would he want to meet me?

542
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:49,670
That...

543
00:37:50,250 --> 00:37:51,360
That day,

544
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:52,700
he happened to be sad,

545
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:54,380
so I had the chance...

546
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:56,300
to talk to him,

547
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:58,780
and he was so kind

548
00:37:59,220 --> 00:38:00,940
that he agreed to play with me.

549
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:02,420
I couldn’t ask for more.

550
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:08,500
Princess.

551
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,130
Princess.

552
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:13,580
His Majesty is grieving

553
00:38:13,860 --> 00:38:15,100
over Noble Consort Zhang’s death

554
00:38:15,300 --> 00:38:17,020
and recalling what she did in the past

555
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:18,300
that she stabbed her arm to pray for rain

556
00:38:18,300 --> 00:38:19,340
and risked her life to protect His Majesty.

557
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:21,620
Proposer of the Hall of Glory

558
00:38:21,620 --> 00:38:22,660
suggests that her funeral

559
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:23,580
be held at the Hall of Imperial Rites.

560
00:38:23,740 --> 00:38:24,860
That’s absurd!

561
00:38:25,260 --> 00:38:26,820
Only the Empress’s funeral

562
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:28,300
can be held there.

563
00:38:32,060 --> 00:38:37,140
= Hall of Happiness and Tranquility =

564
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:43,580
= Feng Jing, courtesy name Dangshi =

565
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:47,100
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =

566
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:19,460
His Majesty says

567
00:39:19,900 --> 00:39:20,900
there will be no court meeting today.

568
00:39:21,540 --> 00:39:23,260
Scholar Feng doesn’t need to draft anything

569
00:39:24,100 --> 00:39:26,020
and can go back to the office to rest.

570
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:33,700
I, Feng Jing,

571
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:36,660
request answers from Your Majesty.

572
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:57,340
That Wang Gongchen who set Scholar Su up

573
00:39:57,340 --> 00:39:58,300
is chumming the waters again.

574
00:39:58,540 --> 00:40:00,140
He proposes that Noble Consort be canonized.

575
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:01,860
The court is resting today,

576
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:03,420
so ministers can’t enter the palace.

577
00:40:03,740 --> 00:40:04,860
Only two officials on duty

578
00:40:05,540 --> 00:40:07,100
can hand in proposals.

579
00:40:08,740 --> 00:40:10,060
Luckily, other than Wang Gongchen

580
00:40:10,060 --> 00:40:11,140
who serves at the Imperial Academy,

581
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:13,100
Imperial Diary Recorder Feng Jing was there.

582
00:40:13,780 --> 00:40:14,980
He drafted a proposal immediately

583
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:16,940
to oppose the canonization.

584
00:40:18,500 --> 00:40:20,340
Both of them became principal
graduates at a young age

585
00:40:20,660 --> 00:40:22,540
and are adored by His Majesty.

586
00:40:23,180 --> 00:40:24,620
His Majesty even betrothed

587
00:40:24,900 --> 00:40:26,300
Prime Minister Yan’s granddaughter,

588
00:40:26,580 --> 00:40:28,340
Prime Minister Fu’s daughter

589
00:40:28,460 --> 00:40:29,740
to Mr. Feng.

590
00:40:30,380 --> 00:40:32,100
He’s been serving as a scholar for years.

591
00:40:33,020 --> 00:40:34,300
Wang Gongchen

592
00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:37,540
left the Capital for that red porcelain incident

593
00:40:38,380 --> 00:40:39,700
but was soon called back.

594
00:40:39,700 --> 00:40:40,460
Your Highness!

595
00:40:47,460 --> 00:40:48,100
Your Highness,

596
00:40:48,340 --> 00:40:49,940
I passed by father’s chamber

597
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:52,060
and saw Wang Gongchen go inside.

598
00:40:52,340 --> 00:40:53,580
Father is going to reprimand him,

599
00:40:53,580 --> 00:40:54,380
isn’t he?

600
00:40:54,460 --> 00:40:55,660
Just like last time, he was demoted

601
00:40:55,740 --> 00:40:57,220
because of that red porcelain incident.

602
00:41:02,140 --> 00:41:04,740
Your father knows what he’s doing.

603
00:41:35,020 --> 00:41:36,380
I just met Huaiji.

604
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:36,980
He said

605
00:41:36,980 --> 00:41:38,580
His Majesty accepted Wang Gongchen’s proposal

606
00:41:38,660 --> 00:41:40,180
and would canonize Noble Consort as the Empress.

607
00:41:40,180 --> 00:41:41,780
The decree will be drafted

608
00:41:41,780 --> 00:41:43,500
after being discussed with ministers tomorrow.

609
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:45,980
How could he?

610
00:41:47,180 --> 00:41:48,020
I’m going to see him.

611
00:41:48,020 --> 00:41:48,660
Huirou.

612
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:52,180
Don’t argue with him.

613
00:41:53,820 --> 00:41:55,260
That’s what Noble Consort Zhang wanted the most

614
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,300
when she was alive

615
00:41:56,900 --> 00:41:57,900
and the last thing

616
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:59,540
your father could do for her.

617
00:42:00,940 --> 00:42:02,260
He won’t change his mind.

618
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:04,020
But Your Highness...

619
00:42:04,140 --> 00:42:05,340
It’s merely an empty title.

620
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:07,980
She’s already dead.

621
00:42:08,660 --> 00:42:09,980
Don’t be too mad.

622
00:42:10,660 --> 00:42:12,020
I’m not mad at her.

623
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:13,540
I’m mad at father.

624
00:42:14,140 --> 00:42:15,580
How could he be so willful?

625
00:42:15,580 --> 00:42:16,500
Stop now!

626
00:42:17,500 --> 00:42:18,940
You’re his daughter.

627
00:42:19,220 --> 00:42:20,860
How could you criticize your father?

628
00:42:21,020 --> 00:42:22,380
Where are your manners?

629
00:42:55,180 --> 00:42:58,300
♪ Isolated kite ♪

630
00:42:58,300 --> 00:43:01,380
♪ Left everything behind ♪

631
00:43:01,380 --> 00:43:04,700
♪ Lost soul ♪

632
00:43:04,700 --> 00:43:07,820
♪ Can’t feel cause he can’t love ♪

633
00:43:07,820 --> 00:43:10,940
♪ Fondness is a beam of light ♪

634
00:43:10,940 --> 00:43:14,060
♪ Shines in the dark ♪

635
00:43:14,100 --> 00:43:17,140
♪ That overshines stars ♪

636
00:43:17,180 --> 00:43:24,020
♪ And nourishes all living things ♪

637
00:43:24,740 --> 00:43:27,460
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

638
00:43:27,460 --> 00:43:31,460
♪ I don’t want to remember, but I can’t forget ♪

639
00:43:31,460 --> 00:43:37,500
♪ My hair turns grey too soon
Laughing at me for being so sentimental ♪

640
00:43:37,500 --> 00:43:40,180
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

641
00:43:40,180 --> 00:43:44,100
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

642
00:43:44,100 --> 00:43:50,500
♪ Towards the direction of light ♪

643
00:43:50,500 --> 00:43:56,700
♪ Light it up for the people ♪

644
00:43:56,700 --> 00:44:02,860
♪ Cure the heartless injury ♪

645
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:18,820
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

646
00:44:18,820 --> 00:44:21,980
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

647
00:44:21,980 --> 00:44:25,140
♪ When and where are we now ♪

648
00:44:25,140 --> 00:44:28,300
♪ I’m left alone, sobbing ♪

649
00:44:28,300 --> 00:44:31,340
♪ I love you so deeply that left
everything behind ♪

650
00:44:31,340 --> 00:44:33,780
♪ Life is always filled
with the sadness of parting ♪

651
00:44:33,780 --> 00:44:37,700
♪ Forget the past and revenge with a smile,
leave all the obsession behind ♪

652
00:44:37,700 --> 00:44:40,940
♪ We look at each other without words ♪

653
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:43,740
♪ Drinking wine with pent-up sadness and love ♪

654
00:44:43,740 --> 00:44:47,180
♪ Those who love more are always
hurt by who love less ♪

